Day 19: Recursion – Factorial, Sum

Find the factorial of a number using recursion.


Find the sum of natural numbers using recursion.


Implement a recursive function to find the Fibonacci sequence.


Implement a recursive function to calculate exponentiation (x^n).


Find the GCD of two numbers using recursion.


Day 20: Recursion – Subsets, Permutations

Generate all subsets of a set using recursion.


Generate all permutations of a string using recursion.


Solve the Tower of Hanoi problem using recursion.


Generate the Pascal's Triangle using recursion.


Find all combinations that sum to a target value using recursion.


Day 21: Review + Mock Test

Implement a recursive binary search.


Find the longest common subsequence between two strings.


Find the unique paths in a grid using recursion.


Implement merging sorted arrays.


Find the maximum product subarray.
